%0 Conference Paper
%T Ẹhugbo Ka! Advancing Machine Translation for the Low-Resource Ẹhugbo Language through Parallel Corpus Development
%A Ukachi Eze-Mbey
%A Uloma Eze-Mbey
%A Ololade Anjuwon
